{"tid":1712978,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"排毒食物：食TG太多者，請注意營養均衡","createTime":"2019-11-12T15:59:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T06:00:57.000Z","uid":331173,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6e71e147f922b862898c028fd440c1a4264f3a4c","tid":1712978,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:59:12.000Z","msg":"雖然唔知TG內有咩毒物，但係食好D點都有D幫助<br />\n以下食材，又平又好食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qdhs0Ub.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqdhs0Ub.png&h=1a6f51fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">吃8大排毒食物，有助去除體重金屬</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 海帶</span><br />\n海帶中的褐藻膠因含水率高，在腸內能形成凝膠狀物質，有助於排除毒素物質，<em>阻止人體吸收鉛、鎘等重金屬，排除體內放射性元素</em>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">2. 番茄</span><br />\n番茄含有豐富的維它命C，而維它命C能排解各種重金屬毒，像是鉻、鋁、鉛等，而番茄有很好的抗氧化還能原能力，可與有毒物質結合，<em>降低體內的重金屬含量</em>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">3. 胡蘿蔔</span><br />\n胡蘿蔔是有效的解毒食物，與體內的汞離子結合之後，<em>能有效降低血液中汞離子的濃度，加速體內汞離子的排出</em>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">4. 大蒜</span><br />\n大蒜中所含的大蒜素，可與鉛結合成為無毒的化合物，能有效<em>防治鉛中毒</em>。此外，大蒜還能提高肝臟的解毒功能，阻斷亞硝胺致癌物質的合成。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">5. 綠豆</span><br />\n綠豆性寒味甘，可<em>解酒毒、野菌毒、砒霜毒、有機磷農藥毒、鉛毒、丹石毒、草木諸毒、鼠藥毒等毒</em>，促進機體的正常代謝。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">6. 地瓜</span><br />\n地瓜含有豐富的膳食纖維，可以吸附食物中的有毒物質，並<em>迅速將毒物帶離腸道，能減緩體內對有毒物質的吸收</em>，是體內環保的好食材。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">7. 南瓜</span><br />\n南瓜中富含的果膠，<em>可以清除體內重金屬和部分農藥</em>，故有防癌防毒的作用；南瓜中富含的鈷是合成胰島素必需的微量元素。南瓜還能消除致癌物質亞硝酸胺的突變作用。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">8. 黑木耳</span><br />\n黑木耳中的植物膠質有較強的吸附力，可將殘留在人體消化系統內的雜質排出體外，起到清胃滌腸的作用。黑木耳<em>對體內難以消化的穀殼、金屬屑等具有溶解作用</em>。<br />\n<br />\n8種最強排毒食物，排除體內重金屬 | Heho健康<br />\n<a href=\"https://heho.com.tw/archives/35824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheho.com.tw%2Farchives%2F35824&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7fPwW8VRzHVpxLRgBu58%2FEQ%3D&h=ca66857a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://heho.com.tw/archives/35824</a>"},{"pid":"48df131bd3a14df95c505a4f7a9f8a4ec0971ddc","tid":1712978,"uid":3865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:00:36.000Z","msg":"有用Post <br />\n幫你推<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8quSsx4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8quSsx4.jpg&h=a064044b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"490ab27162367c56e299f87f6c1cbe93734b70a8","tid":1712978,"uid":36866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:00:57.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"215eeefa79e9f2eaf1f4806f35555e684ad7e953","tid":1712978,"uid":203086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:01:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c928142456e007d096d64a2b585468f380d1f374","tid":1712978,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:14:33.000Z","msg":"係呀，解&amp;排重金屬可能有D用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔知TG成份係乜"},{"pid":"4b443ff1b2cd1672368bfa23ca528cf2491059d0","tid":1712978,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:11:32.000Z","msg":"雖然係殘體字但係呢篇唔錯，穴位清肺熱！<br />\n我岩岩試過掂呀，按左兩三下己經見效（病左就快一星期）<br />\n<br />\n我聽聞有好多人聞完TG之後都有便秘，咁應該岩左以下症狀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">肺火旺的症状</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1、<em>&ldquo;肺開竅於鼻&rdquo;</em>，由此可知&ldquo;肺火&rdquo;表現在鼻子上面，因為肺主呼吸所以通過鼻子來與外部溝通聯繫。 &ldquo;肺火&rdquo;的產生伴隨著以下的症狀：初期是口乾舌燥,流鼻血,然後會出現咽喉疼痛再甚者會出現咯血的症狀,最後症狀在臉部的表現是長痘痘等由於乾燥引起的。<br />\n2、臉有癤子，咽乾疼痛、咳嗽胸痛、乾咳無痰或痰少而黏、潮熱盜汗、手足心熱、失眠、舌紅。<br />\n3、很容易傷風，而且傷風後出現高熱、咳嗽、痰黃稠而粘、舌紅苔黃等症狀。<br />\n4、一些小孩睡覺時蓋不住被子，喜歡俯臥，喜吃冷飲，口唇發紅，也是肺火旺的表現。<br />\n5、腸胃症狀表現為胃部灼熱疼痛、腹脹、口乾口臭、大便稀爛、便秘、牙齦腫痛、胃口不好等。胃火還分虛實兩種,虛火表現為輕微咳嗽、胃口不好、便秘、腹脹、舌紅、少苔;實火表現為上腹不適、口乾口苦、大便乾硬。*<br />\n<br />\n*另一篇文講，因為肺熱會抽乾腸嘅水份，所以連腸都會乾埋。"},{"pid":"af8215e383167fc93e03b2aa04e5e706e3a7611e","tid":1712978,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:15:07.000Z","msg":"咁穴位按邊呢？ 我岩岩試左3， 好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">按摩清肺火穴位</span><br />\n1、清肺火按摩合谷穴<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X7XpoNu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX7XpoNu.jpg&h=2dbfec99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2、清肺火按摩尺泽穴<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KJWEW7u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKJWEW7u.jpg&h=c63926b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3、清肺火按摩迎香穴<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tAzOQsu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtAzOQsu.jpg&h=36e3c986&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSOURCE：<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/29191947\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzhuanlan.zhihu.com%2Fp%2F29191947&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7fPwW8VRzHVpxLRgBu58%2FEQ%3D&h=b194cc7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/29191947</a>"},{"pid":"717bd828662dc16ee3acae8570e6dbf79d383d26","tid":1712978,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:23:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">清肺火的六大食物</span></span><em>中醫角度</em><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">1、梨*</span>：梨性涼，味甘，能清熱化痰，熱咳者宜之。<br />\n<em>*雪梨，貢梨。凡白色嘅梨。絕對有效</em><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">2、羅漢果**</span>：羅漢果有清肺利咽的作用,適用於肺熱引起的咽炎、咽喉腫痛。<br />\n<em>**沖水</em><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">3、枇杷***</span>：枇杷性涼，味甘，能潤肺化痰止咳。<br />\n<em>***枇杷膏</em><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">4、柿子</span>：鮮柿生食能改善咳嗽痰多、虛勞咯血紅軟熟柿,可治療熱病煩渴、口乾唇爛、心中煩熱等。柿子所具有的潤肺止咳、清熱生津、化痰軟堅的功效,適合冬季食用。<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">5、甘蔗****</span>：甘蔗味甘，平，無毒，有滋陰潤燥、和胃止嘔、清熱解毒之功效，對於因陰液不足所導致口乾、咳嗽痰少、大便秘結等症，可利用多食甘蔗來改善症狀<em><br />\n****竹蔗茅根精，絕對方便有效夾平。鮮拃蔗汁，未試過但應該都得。</em><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">6、川貝母</span>：川貝母含有多種生物鹼、甾醇及澱粉等，性味甘苦微寒，清熱、潤肺、化痰，對多種咳嗽都有良好的效果,是化痰止咳的要藥。"},{"pid":"fe10032ea0235abbfcd8a73dadf8d61a7982ab74","tid":1712978,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:26:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">清肺火的應注意</span></span>中醫角度<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">1、忌辛辣食物</span><br />\n俗話說的好預防勝於治療,胃火大多半是由於飲食不當導致,例如辛辣食物,酗酒,都會助火生熱,使得胃火旺盛,平時我們盡量避免使用辛辣食物,這樣就可能降低胃火。<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">2、保證睡眠質量</span><br />\n身體過度疲勞會導致上火,再加上睡眠質量不好,更會火上加火,每天要注意睡覺時間,身體在休息的時候也是排毒的時候,如果此時休息不好影響身體排毒,會使得毒素殘留體內,導致身體上火,所以保證睡眠質量很重要。<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">3、補充水分</span><br />\n俗話說的好，水火不容，可見水對火是有克製作用的，當你感覺自己胃火大的時候,可以多喝水，喝水不但能夠解決胃火大的問題，還能解決其他很多問題，要不怎麼有&ldquo;白開水治百病&rdquo;的說法。<br />\n<br />\n生活中要注意勞逸結合,飲食上要注意多吃含維生素的蔬菜水果,多喝水少喝酸甜飲料,少吃辛辣煎炸食品,少抽煙喝酒。胃火、肝火、肺火和心理狀態也有密不可分的關係,保持樂觀積極的生活態度其實是人們在乾燥冬日里最好的滅火劑。<br />\nsource：<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/29191947\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzhuanlan.zhihu.com%2Fp%2F29191947&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7fPwW8VRzHVpxLRgBu58%2FEQ%3D&h=b194cc7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/29191947</a>"},{"pid":"86942c8c83f43cbf0b68a3a7f405f4ef6352e77e","tid":1712978,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:06:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">原來載豬咀都無用，皮膚會吸收</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30QeVjF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30QeVjF.jpg&h=919822de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">著化學保護衣</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1ef3d64e3f02e1437aae1d7ef604ec9023b9f9d6","tid":1712978,"uid":204227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:22:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d12c4c5f19a35f1af50a00545d5d570e3e60ef5","tid":1712978,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:00:57.000Z","msg":"TG毒不能解，可殘留身體超廿年<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1722350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1722350</a>"}]}